    <p>✨ At Dimple’s, we handle your nails with care and artistry.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content hidden" id="contactSection">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Email: nails@dimple.com</p>
    <p>Phone: 123-456-7890</p>
